title: Ep 33 - Say Yes to EVERYTHING
itunes:title: Ep 33 - Say Yes to EVERYTHING
description:
Saying no keeps us in our comfort zone and that will limit our experiences. If we want to do, experience and become more we must push ourselves out of our comfort zones. In this episode Rob talks about his challenge to himself to say yes to everything and makes a challenge for you to do the same.
